structure: Day 1: Booster Draft (3x Modern Horizons); 3 rounds of in-pod Swiss play; 5 rounds of Swiss (Modern); cut to 12 points
Day 2: Booster Draft; 3 rounds of in-pod Swiss play; 5 rounds of Swiss (Modern); cut to Top 8
Modern legal sets: Mirrodin – War of the Spark, Eighth Edition – Core Set 2020, Modern Horizons (66 sets)
Mulligan: London (any number of times, always draw seven cards, then return cards to the bottom equal to the number of mulligans taken)
name: Mythic Championship IV 2019
